in the cohesive way

00:03:03.980 --> 00:03:05.930
that it was solved
the first time.

00:03:05.930 --> 00:03:08.710
And designer as curator
puts the responsibility

00:03:08.710 --> 00:03:10.190
to design on everyone.

00:03:10.190 --> 00:03:12.710
So everyone understands
the design problem.

00:03:12.710 --> 00:03:18.000
Everyone can actually contribute
mocks and contribute assets,

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:21.920
and I've kind of seen
that designers that

00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:24.500
